.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-LISTFORWARDS-OFFERED-RATE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-listforwards-offered-rate \- FEAT-2701 node-listforwards-offered-rate
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-listforwards-offered-rate
.SH DESCRIPTION
Reports the ratio of offered forwards to total forwards for this node (FEAT-2701).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN containing \fBoffered_rate\fR (float), \fBoffered\fR (int), and \fBtotal\fR (int).
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
